          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">Does insurance cover waterproofing?</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
            Preventive waterproofing typically isn't covered, but we help with claims for existing water damage. Many insurers offer premium discounts for homes with proper waterproofing.
